Background:
Ethan is a 34-year-old tech professional who has carved out a successful career in the rapidly evolving world of software development. With a keen eye for problem-solving and a passion for innovation, Ethan has climbed the corporate ladder, honing his skills and taking on increasingly complex projects that challenge him both intellectually and creatively.

Demographics:
